{"tid":351182,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發現接近30或者30歲以上既單身女人都好有問題","createTime":"2017-08-07T20:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T13:21:01.000Z","uid":103380,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da37de3609e1f9f3259567a3e91fc3aa0613706f","tid":351182,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T20:13:16.000Z","msg":"讀書/出黎做野都遇唔少呢啲女人<br />\n係咪幾廿年都係老處 精神有少少失常<br />\n<br />\n呢啲咁既單身女人 <br />\n<br />\n一類係化到好濃妝 整個線色/藍色既眼影<br />\n講野講到好溫柔 懶係斯斯文文 但係就唔係投訴依樣就投訴個樣<br />\n<br />\n一類就係野蠻過閪 當正所有男人死撚左佢全家咁<br />\n或者啲候生既靚女係佢情敵 又係投訴佢 針對佢<br />\n<br />\n有冇人覺得 定係我多疑 啲<br />\n上左年紀單身女人真係好麻煩<br />\n<br />\n利申 男 冇比以上所講既女人惹過 淨係一直以黎留意到"},{"pid":"ba6e736b89b1346c746259e0463ffedab49f6207","tid":351182,"uid":82720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"Ali?"},{"pid":"96baa4658126fe8d6033f6b93b313809af50f44f","tid":351182,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ali?</blockquote><br />\n部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec880fb13d41b688d1b6eaa99f2df268fc75cb7","tid":351182,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"單身既9成9係<br />\n唔係單身有d都好好人"},{"pid":"40c06846eee1d7b9be6079d0e069b6475026d9c3","tid":351182,"uid":65979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:38:26.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"7155b4d26558305f84646d665728a5d7ea069cdc","tid":351182,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單身既9成9係<br />\n唔係單身有d都好好人</blockquote><br />\n係咪真係冇愛 個人會易燥同心理唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648b651031fa7ebf7dd432e69a8771a8195d3b00","tid":351182,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9ff11c55281b3097f383abaa9ad90c5e660